high_descs: Turn to the right and walk over to the window.
Pick up the green rag that is on the floor below the window.
Turn completely around, make a right at the dresser, and walk over to face the dresser.
Place the rag on the credit card that is to the right of the pen.
Turn to the right, walk a few steps, then turn left to face the window again.
Pick up the white rag from the floor in front of the window.
Turn around, make a right past the dresser and walk over to face the dresser.
Place the white rag in front of the credit card that is to the left of the pen on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move two rags from the floor to the dresser.
